728174f-b.text: Vleigh Place, at about 71st Avenue. View 1 is in a northeasterly direction across the fields and farmhouses grouped around the area of Vleigh Place and Kissena Boulevard. View 2 shows a farm with a sprinkler system on the west side of Vleigh Place, near 71st Avenue. This area was later developed into a modern residential neighborhood. March 3, 1937. Views 1,2
